        <num>CC 1404</num>
        <heading>1404.  Rescission inadmissible against sale of succession rights</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1404.  Rescission inadmissible against sale of succession rights.
The action of rescission is not admitted against a sale of successive rights, made without fraud to one of the heirs and at his risk by the other coheirs or any of them.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=108759</p>
